    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab><persName><name ref="Cuneradus">Cuneradu</name></persName>, avitator in
                            <placeName ref="#places/3243">loco Alfiano</placeName>, prope <placeName
                            ref="#places/3243">Vico Fitri</placeName>, filio <persName>bone memorie
                                <name ref="Gauseramus">Chauserami</name></persName> riceve da
                            <persName ref="#people/214" key="#Bishops">Gherardus</persName> gratia
                        Dei huius Sancte Lucanem ecclesiam humulis <rs key="#Bishops">episcopus</rs>
                        per cartula livellario nomine ad censum perexolvendum (…) <rs
                            key="#Churches">ecclesiam</rs> illa cuius vocabulum est beati <orgName
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1709" key="#Churches">Sancti Angeli</orgName>,
                        sitas loco <placeName ref="#places/2718" key="#Churches"
                            >Corsanicho</placeName>, pertenens <rs key="#Monasteries"
                            >monasterio</rs>
                        <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/228" key="#Monasteries">Sancte
                            Marie</orgName>, sitas <placeName ref="#places/4" key="#Cities #Rivers"
                            >foras <rs key="#Cities">civitate</rs> ista Lucense</placeName>, prope
                            <rs key="#Rivers">fluvio Auserclo</rs>, quod est de suppotestatem ipsius
                            <rs key="#Mother_churches">episcopatui</rs>] vestro <orgName
                            ref="#juridical_persons/68" key="#Mother_churches">Sancti
                            Martini</orgName>, iam dicta ecclesia Sancti Angeli una cum casis
                        domnicatis quam et massariciis cum fundamentis (…) omnia quantum ad ipsa
                        ecclesia est pertinentes (…); simul et (…) duo <rs key="#Wine">petie de
                            vineis</rs> et una <rs key="#Petiae #Landed_possessions">petia de
                            terra</rs> in ipso loco <placeName ref="#places/2718"
                            key="#Petiae #Landed_possessions #Wine">Corsanico</placeName>,
                        pertenentes ipsius <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterium</rs>
                        <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/228" key="#Monasteries">Sancte
                            Marie</orgName>: suprascripte duo petie de vinee et predicta petia de
                        terra in integrum; adque (…) quattuor casis et rebus massariciis illis in
                        loco <placeName ref="#places/2104">Feruniano</placeName>, prope <rs
                            key="#Baptismal_churches">plebem</rs>
                        <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/1702" key="#Baptismal_churches">Sancti
                            Stefani</orgName>, pertenentes suprascripti <rs key="#Monasteries"
                            >monasterii</rs>
                        <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/228" key="#Monasteries">Sancte
                            Marie</orgName>, qui una ex ipse casa recta esse videtur per
                                <persName><name ref="Martinulus">Martinulo</name></persName>, et
                        ille secunda recta esse videtur per <persName><name ref="Venerandulus"
                                >Venerandulo</name></persName>, et illa tertia recta esse videtur
                        per <persName><name ref="Maginbertulus">Magnipertulo</name></persName>, et
                        ille quarte recta esse videtur per <persName><name ref="Ildibertulus"
                                >Ildipertulo</name></persName>; suprascriptis quatuor casis cum
                        fundamentis, curtis, ortis ecc. (…); una cum casa illa domnicata in predicto
                        loco <placeName ref="#places/2104">Feruniano</placeName>, pertenentes
                        suprascripti monasterii, casa ipsa domnicata cum curte, granario, orto,
                        terris, ecc. (…); simul et (…) casa et res illa in loco <placeName
                            ref="#places/3124">Vualleccle</placeName>, qui pertinens suprascripti
                        monasterio et <persName><name ref="Gumbertus">Gumperto</name></persName> eas
                        ad manus suas abere videtur, casa ipsa cum fundamento, curte, orto, terris
                        ecc. (…); una cum casa et res illa in loco ubi dicitur <placeName
                            ref="#places/3328">Massacuculi</placeName>, qui pertinens suprascripti
                            <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterii</rs>
                        <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/228" key="#Monasteries">Sancte
                            Marie</orgName>; casa ipsa cum terris ecc., omnia quantum (…) <persName
                            key="#Agricultural_workers"><name ref="Ermulus">Ermulo</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Agricultural_workers">massario</rs> exinde ad manus suas abuit in
                        integrum; simul et (…) casa et res illa in loco <placeName
                            ref="#places/3336">Vetuliano</placeName>, qui regitur per <persName
                            key="#Agricultural_workers"><name ref="Silvulus"
                            >Silvulo</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Agricultural_workers">massario</rs>, pertinentes suprascripti <rs
                            key="#Monasteries">monasteri</rs>
                        <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/228" key="#Monasteries">Sancte
                            Marie</orgName>, iam dicta casa una cum omnia res ad eam pertinentes
                        (…); una cum casa et res illa in loco <placeName ref="#places/395"
                            >Rocta</placeName>, prope <rs key="#Churches">ecclesie</rs>
                        <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/3322" key="#Churches">Domini et
                            Salvatoris</orgName>, pertenentes ipsius <rs key="#Monasteries"
                            >monasterii</rs>
                        <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/228" key="#Monasteries">Sancte
                            Marie</orgName> et modo recta esse videtur per <persName
                            key="#Agricultural_workers"><name ref="Insuardulus"
                            >Insuardolo</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Agricultural_workers">massario</rs>, casa ipsa una cum omnia res
                        ad eam pertenentes (…); adque et (…) duo casis et rebus massariciis illis in
                        loco ubi dicitur <placeName ref="#places/2112">Novam</placeName>, prope <rs
                            key="#Baptismal_churches">plebem</rs>
                        <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/1710" key="#Baptismal_churches">Sancti
                            Saturnini</orgName>, qui sunt pertenentes ipsius monasterii, qui una ex
                        ipse recta esse videtur per <persName key="#Agricultural_workers"><name
                                ref="Ragibaldus">Rachipaldo</name></persName> et <persName
                            key="#Agricultural_workers"><name ref="Baldo">Paldo</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Agricultural_workers">massarii</rs> (…); una cum una <rs
                            key="#Wine">petia de vinea</rs> mea illa in loco <placeName
                            ref="#places/3125" key="#Wine">Mutiliano</placeName>, quas
                                <persName><name ref="Ragibrandulus">Rachiprandulo</name></persName>
                        eas ad manus suas abet, qui pertinentes suprascripti monasteri Sancte Marie,
                        petia ipsa in integrum; adque et (…) una petia de terra illa in <placeName
                            ref="#places/2124"
                            key="#Confinia #Petiae #Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Mention #Roads #Count"
                            >loco Vuindal[..]</placeName>, quas <persName><name ref="Adalbertulus"
                                >Adalpertulo</name></persName> ad manus suas abet, pertenentes
                        suprascripti monasteri Sancte Marie, qui uno caput tenet in <rs key="#Roads"
                            >via publica</rs> et alio caput tenet cum ambas lateras in <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Mention">terra <persName
                                key="#Confinia #Landed_possessions #Count" ref="#people/1514"
                                >Adalberti</persName>
                            <rs key="#Count">comes</rs></rs>, petia ipsa in integrum; una cum alia
                        petia de terra in loco ubi dicitur <placeName key="#Hay/fodder"
                            >Pratulo</placeName> pertenentes suprascripti monasteri Sancte Marie qui
                        uno caput tenet in via publica et alio caput tenet in terra <persName><name
                                ref="Ildebrandus">Ildiprandi</name></persName>, petia ipsa in
                        integrum; seo et (…) <rs key="#Petiae">duo petiole de terra</rs> ille in
                        loco <placeName ref="#places/4" key="#Cities #Petiae">foras <rs
                                key="#Cities">civitatem</rs> ista Lucense</placeName>, qui pertinens
                        ipsius monasteri Sancte Marie […34…], una ex ipse est tenente uno caput in
                        terra ecclesie <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/3300"
                            key="#Confinia #Landed_possessions #Churches">Sancti Alesandri</orgName>
                        […34…] <persName><name ref="Giselfredus">Ghiselfridi</name></persName> [……],
                        petiole ipse in integrum; una cum <rs key="#Churches">ecclesia</rs> illa cui
                        vocabulum est [<orgName ref="#juridical_persons/1701" key="#Churches">Beati
                            Sancti Georgi</orgName>, sita in loco] <placeName ref="#places/2104"
                            >Feruniano</placeName>, pertenentes ipsius monasteri Sancte Marie,
                        suprascripta ecclesia […16…] Sancti G[eorgi …… una cum ali]a petiola de
                        terra in eodem loco ubi dicitur ad <placeName ref="#places/3335"
                            >Pruno</placeName>, pertenentes ipsius monasteri Sancte Marie, […15…] in
                        via publica, petia ipsa in integrum. Il livello è per Cunerado una cum
                                <persName><name>Karoini</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name>Peritei</name></persName> germani filii mei vel de
                        eorum heredes sint (…) suprascripta ecclesia Sancti Angeli et rebus ad eam
                        pertinentibus cum omnibus casis et rebus. Obbligo di miglioramento. Censo
                        (pro omni censum et iustitia): ad pars suprascripti monasteri Sancte Marie,
                        per singulos annos in mense augusto ad ministeriale vestro, quas inibi pro
                        tempore fuerit (…) argentum denarios novem boni expendivilis; et hominibus
                        illis in ipsis casis abitantes fuerit, eos a mandato vestro hic Luca venire
                        faciamus legem et iustitiam faciendum tantum (…). Pena: argentum solidos
                        ducentos (…). <persName key="#Writer #Notary"><name>Lopo</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> scrive due <rs
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis">cartulas</rs>. Actum <placeName
                            ref="#places/4" key="#Churches #Mother_churches #Bishops"
                            >Luca</placeName>.</ab>
                    <ab>Sottoscrivono come <rs key="#Witness">testimoni</rs>:</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
